name: Women Support Women
description:
Women are supposed to support other women, but in reality we know that what is evil to women is often from the women themselves. 

While seeing other women more beautiful, successful, and superior, not a few of the women who should be supportive and proud, instead sneer and vilify each other.

The competition between women is so tight that it often happens that one steps on and drowns the other to make it look perfect.
